{{Lunisolar March}} '''March 18''' is the 18th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Kenchō|ja|建長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1249]] {{ill|May 2|ja|5月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The era name was changed from {{ill|Hōji|ja|宝治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to {{ill|Kenchō|ja|建長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * {{ill|Man'en|ja|万延|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1860]] {{ill|April 8|ja|4月8日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Due to the occurrence of the {{ill|Sakuradamon Incident|ja|桜田門外の変|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the era name was changed from {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to {{ill|Man'en|ja|万延|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Births == * {{ill|Genki (era)|ja|元亨|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1573]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Doi Toshikatsu|ja|土井利勝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, Tairō and the first daimyō of the Furukawa Domain in Kazusa (died [[1644]]). * [[Shunji]] 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1654]] {{ill|May 4|ja|5月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kangxi Emperor|ja|康熙帝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 4th Emperor of the Qing dynasty (died [[1722]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Bunmei|ja|文明|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1473]] {{ill|April 15|ja|4月15日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Yamana Sōzen|ja|山名宗全|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (also known as Yamana Mochitoyo) – a regional warlord (born [[1404]]).
