'''March 18''' is the 18th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|qq=|12=draft}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|qq=|12=draft}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Kenchō|ja|建長|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[1249]] {{ill|May 2|ja|5月2日|qq=|12=draft}}) – The era name was changed from {{ill|Hōji|ja|宝治|qq=|12=draft}} to {{ill|Kenchō|ja|建長|qq=|12=draft}}.
* {{ill|Man'en|ja|万延|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1860]] {{ill|April 8|ja|4月8日|qq=|12=draft}}) – Due to the occurrence of the {{ill|Sakuradamon Incident|ja|桜田門外の変|qq=|12=draft}}, the era name was changed from {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|12=draft}} to {{ill|Man'en|ja|万延|qq=|12=draft}}.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Genki (era)|ja|元亨|qq=|12=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[1573]] {{ill|April 19|ja|4月19日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Doi Toshikatsu|ja|土井利勝|qq=|12=draft}}, Tairō and the first daimyō of the Furukawa Domain in Kazusa (died [[1644]]).
* [[Shunji]] 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1654]] {{ill|May 4|ja|5月4日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kangxi Emperor|ja|康熙帝|qq=|12=draft}}, the 4th Emperor of the Qing dynasty (died [[1722]]).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Bunmei|ja|文明|qq=|12=draft}} 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[1473]] {{ill|April 15|ja|4月15日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Yamana Sōzen|ja|山名宗全|qq=|12=draft}} (also known as Yamana Mochitoyo) – a regional warlord (born [[1404]]).

