== Births == * [[:en:Genkō (1321–1324)|Genki (era)]] 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1573|1573]] [[:en:April 19|April 19]]) – [[:en:Doi Toshikatsu|Doi Toshikatsu]], Tairō and the first daimyō of the Furukawa Domain in Kazusa (died [[:en:1644|1644]]). * [[Shunji]] 11th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1654]] [[:en:May 4|May 4]]) – [[:en:Kangxi Emperor|Kangxi Emperor]], the 4th Emperor of the Qing dynasty (died [[1722]]).
== Deaths == * [[:en:Civilization|Bunmei]] 5th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1473|1473]] [[:en:April 15|April 15]]) – [[:en:Yamana Sōzen|Yamana Sōzen]] (also known as Yamana Mochitoyo) – a regional warlord (born [[:en:1404|1404]]).
