'''March 18''' is the 18th day of the month {{ill|March (Lunisolar)|ja|3月 (旧暦)|lt=March (Yayoi)|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/March (Lunisolar)|qq=}}, the 3rd month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Rokuyō|qq=}} day is {{ill|Tomobiki|qid=Q96759840|1=tomobiki}}{{efn|ja|友引|1=Rokuyō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q9418169}}{{efn|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tomobiki|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 六曜|1=Rokuyō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q9418169}}.

== Events ==
* {{ill|Kenchō|en|Kenchō|qid=Q1194270|lt=Kenchō|1=Kenchō}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1249|en|1249|qid=Q5485|lt=1249|1=1249}} {{ill|May 2|en|May 2|qid=Q2545|lt=May 2|1=May 2}}) – The era name was changed from {{ill|Hōji (era)|en|Hōji (era)|qid=Q1327400|lt=Hōji|1=Hōji (era)}} to {{ill|Kenchō|en|Kenchō|qid=Q1194270|lt=Kenchō|1=Kenchō}}.
* {{ill|Man'en|en|Man'en|qid=Q1193862|lt=Man'en|1=Man'en}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1860|en|1860|qid=Q7691|lt=1860|1=1860}} {{ill|April 8|en|April 8|qid=Q2503|lt=April 8|1=April 8}}) – Due to the occurrence of the {{ill|Sakuradamon Incident (1860)|en|Sakuradamon Incident (1860)|qid=Q46603|lt=Sakuradamon Incident|1=Sakuradamon Incident (1860)}}, the era name was changed from {{ill|Ansei|en|Ansei|qid=Q1327259|lt=Ansei|1=Ansei}} to {{ill|Man'en|en|Man'en|qid=Q1193862|lt=Man'en|1=Man'en}}.

== Births ==
* {{ill|Genkō (1321–1324)|en|Genkō (1321–1324)|qid=Q509889|lt=Genki (era)|1=Genkō (1321–1324)}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1573|en|1573|qid=Q6678|lt=1573|1=1573}} {{ill|April 19|en|April 19|qid=Q2523|lt=April 19|1=April 19}}) – {{ill|Doi Toshikatsu|en|Doi Toshikatsu|qid=Q1042428|lt=Doi Toshikatsu|1=Doi Toshikatsu}}, Tairō and the first daimyō of the Furukawa Domain in Kazusa (died {{ill|1644|en|1644|qid=Q6920|lt=1644|1=1644}}).
* {{ill|Shunji|en|Shunji|qid=Q7505077|lt=Shunji|1=Shunji}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1654|en|1654|qid=Q6970|lt=1654|1=1654}} {{ill|May 4|en|May 4|qid=Q2549|lt=May 4|1=May 4}}) – {{ill|Kangxi Emperor|en|Kangxi Emperor|qid=Q17790|lt=Kangxi Emperor|1=Kangxi Emperor}}, the 4th Emperor of the Qing dynasty (died {{ill|1722|en|1722|qid=Q6918|lt=1722|1=1722}}).

== Deaths ==
* {{ill|Civilization|en|Civilization|qid=Q8432|lt=Bunmei|1=Civilization}} 5th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1473|en|1473|qid=Q6594|lt=1473|1=1473}} {{ill|April 15|en|April 15|qid=Q2497|lt=April 15|1=April 15}}) – {{ill|Yamana Sōzen|en|Yamana Sōzen|qid=Q1355689|lt=Yamana Sōzen|1=Yamana Sōzen}} (also known as Yamana Mochitoyo) – a regional warlord (born {{ill|1404|en|1404|qid=Q6121|lt=1404|1=1404}}).

